{"id":806617,"url":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_One_and_Only_Ivan_(movie)","text":"\"The One and Only Ivan\" is a 2020 American fantasy drama movie directed by Thea Sharrock. It is based on the children's novel of the same name by K. A. Applegate.\nIt is inspired by the true story of Ivan the gorilla. The movie stars the voices of Sam Rockwell as Ivan alongside Angelina Jolie, Danny DeVito, Helen Mirren, Brooklynn Prince, Chaka Khan, Ron Funches, Phillipa Soo, and Mike White with human characters played by Ram\u00F3n Rodr\u00EDguez, Ariana Greenblatt, and Bryan Cranston.","categories":[],"infobox_types":["film"],"annotations":[{"uri":"Fantasy","surface_form":"fantasy","offset":43},{"uri":"Drama","surface_form":"drama","offset":51},{"uri":"Thea_Sharrock","surface_form":"Thea Sharrock","offset":75},{"uri":"The_One_and_Only_Ivan","surface_form":"children's novel","offset":109},{"uri":"K._A._Applegate","surface_form":"K. A. Applegate","offset":146},{"uri":"Ivan_(gorilla)","surface_form":"Ivan the gorilla","offset":199},{"uri":"Sam_Rockwell","surface_form":"Sam Rockwell","offset":247},{"uri":"Angelina_Jolie","surface_form":"Angelina Jolie","offset":278},{"uri":"Danny_DeVito","surface_form":"Danny DeVito","offset":294},{"uri":"Helen_Mirren","surface_form":"Helen Mirren","offset":308},{"uri":"Brooklynn_Prince","surface_form":"Brooklynn Prince","offset":322},{"uri":"Chaka_Khan","surface_form":"Chaka Khan","offset":340},{"uri":"Ron_Funches","surface_form":"Ron Funches","offset":352},{"uri":"Phillipa_Soo","surface_form":"Phillipa Soo","offset":365},{"uri":"Mike_White_(filmmaker)","surface_form":"Mike White","offset":383},{"uri":"Ram%C3%B3n_Rodr%C3%ADguez_(actor)","surface_form":"Ram\u00F3n Rodr\u00EDguez","offset":426},{"uri":"Bryan_Cranston","surface_form":"Bryan Cranston","offset":466}]}